"My government is strongly committed to reducing violence," said Pena Nieto to US President Barack Obama at the Oval Office earlier this week.
I will propose a new security strategy with which we can achieve this objective.
Pena Nieto was a governor of his home state, Mexico, before he was on an equal footing with the US president.
In this densely populated, extensive part of the country surrounding the capital, opinions about the new head of state are shared.
A Direct Man
